title: PS3 Rebug CFW kit 4.41.2 3.55.4 999 downgrader multiMAN PS2Class
description:
Custom firmware kit for PS3. <a href=" http://rebug.me/rebug-3-55-3-and-4-21-1-rex-editions-and-999-downgrader/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://rebug.me/rebug-3-55-3-and-4-21-1-rex-editions-and-999-downgrader/</a>

Included:
* Rebug 4.41.2 LITE
* Rebug 3.55.4 REX
* "9.99" downgrader
* multiMAN 4.40 BASE (update server working as of 2013-07-02)

NOTE: You can check the status of QA flag using Rebug Toolkit.
1. Go to "* Package Manager" => "Install Package Files" => "PS3 Hard Disk"
2. Install "REBUG-TOOLBOX" package
3. Run Rebug Toolbox from XMB and scroll right to "Utilities"
4. "Toggle QA Flag" should be set to "Enabled"

Also included for your convenience:
* PS2Classics Placeholder R3 1.00
* reactPSN 2.26
Follow instructions in PS2Classics/README.txt
